text: Patryk Wolanski (born 15 August 1991 in Poland) is a Polish footballer who currently plays as a Goalkeeper for Widzew Łódź in Poland.Patryk Wolański ponownie piłkarzem Widzewa! Widzew Łódź ==Career== Wolanski started his senior career with Widzew Łódź in the Polish Ekstraklasa, where he made sixteen appearances and scored zero goals. After that, he played for Midtjylland, Vejle Boldklub, and AC Horsens. == References == == External links == * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Polish footballers Category:Widzew Łódź players Category:FC Midtjylland players Category:Vejle Boldklub players Category:AC Horsens players Category:Association football goalkeepers
